page.title: 20BENENDEN WEALD, ENDING.
page.content: The group which did this project is made up of girls from the sixth-form of Benenden School, studying geography for Advanced Level. The field work was done in July l985 by:- Lucinda Aitken, Mary-Louise Gurdon, photographer, Mary Harper, Alexandra Higgins, Philippa Myers, Sally Nevard, Harreit Purser. We were assisted by many including Kate Strong, and the warden of Swattenden Centre. The family at Forest Farm was most co-opertive, for which we are very grateful, as we also are to Damien Sanderson for sorting out our difficulties with the computer. Mary Thomas.
